Hi radioman,

Another question:
In your version DelteOlderThan is only implemented on the primairy cache and not on the secondairy. What happens with a tile in the secondairy if the same tile in the primairy cache is deleted?

Marcel
tile will be loaded from secondary cache and therefore will be added back to primary

What is the reason DeleteOlderThan on secondairy cache is not implemented in your version of GMap?

I have also created to methods to Delete a entire map from primairy or secundairy cache.
This is handy when a complete tile server is updated.
